id: 2715
name: "The Executor"
power: 2.0
text: |
  The Executor is an elected office responsible for managing assets
  in the Lost and Found Department.

  The Executor SHOULD maintain administrative regulations specifying
  how e will manage such assets. The Executor is ENCOURAGED to draft
  eir administrative regulations such that any actions e takes to
  manage such assets occur no less frequently than quarterly.
